Starstomp still in bot mode, came up to what seemed to be a terminal. 
She tried to turn it on, but it lacked power. She then plugged herself 
to it so she could boost it up and make it work. It started working 
and she quickly found a plan of the ship. She opened a commline to 
nightlight and aerotaur:
-Guys, I found a map of this spacecraft. I'm transmitting it to you 
now. I'm going to the cr chamber, I'm near to it.
